snippet.title: Praetorians HD Remaster - Gamescom Trailer
snippet.description:
Lead the emerging Roman Empire by proving a legionnaire's worth on the battlefields of Egypt, the combat theaters of Gaul and the heart of the Roman Empire in Italy, in a crusade to become Emperor. Praetorians HD Remaster is slated for release in Q4 2019 for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC.

Watch more trailers here!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vvB2wiDUDdA&list=PLaQokWZfgbynLRhV7HigqcfVAzsNB-t6b&index=1
